            Termit

    Simple terminal emulator based on vte library.

    Features:
        * tabs
        * bookmarks
        * changing tab name
        * changing font for tabs
        * encodings (all available from GTK2)
        * sessions

    Configuration can be changed via $HOME/.config/termit/termit.cfg file (example is provided).
    
    Command-line arguments:
        * --version (-v) - prints version info
        * --session=[sess.file] - load session at startup
        * --command=[cmd] - start using command (also -c)

    Useful keys:
        * Ctrl-t - open tab
        * Ctrl-w - close tab
        * double-click on tab bar - open tab
        * Ctrl-Ins - copy to buffer
        * Shift-Ins - paste from buffer

